description: Proteome analyses of skeletal muscles from 12 male C57BL/6J mouse (microgravity with fructo-oligosaccharide (FOS) ingestion, microgravity without FOS ingestion,  artificial 1 g with FOS ingestion,and artificial 1 g without FOS ingestion, [n=3, respectively]) were carried out tryptic digestion followed by LC-MS/MS analysis (DDA). The obtained results were searched against UniProt DB by Mascot, and the identified peptides were filtered at 1% FDR threshold by searching against the randomized decoy DB.
